{"about_the_game":"In the year 20XX, the simulator developed by Non-Bald Technology was officially launched. This product can simulate a hundred days of exam preparation within a single day, assisting students in improving their scores.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/dongtu-export.gif?t=1693206347\" /><br>Players will assume the role of a student who has just received the simulator. They will continuously refine their exam preparation strategy within the simulator.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Improve academic performance</h2>Enhance memory, and absorb more knowledge into your mind!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/mind.gif?t=1693206347\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Plan your daily routine</h2>While studying is important, it's also crucial not to overwork yourself. Maintain your physical and mental well-being by planning proper rest and relaxation time every day!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/TIME.gif?t=1693206347\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Organize your backpack</h2>Bring the necessary items and food, and make the most of every inch of space!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/bag.gif?t=1693206347\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Maintain a balanced diet</h2>A full stomach is essential for optimal learning!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/cook.gif?t=1693206347\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Engage in regular physical exercise</h2>Actively participate in sports and activities to keep your body energized!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705420/extras/tug.gif?t=1693206347\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Relax and unwind your mind</h2>It is es